data.description:
PRICED TO SELL AT $ 295,000 ONLY !! Perfect Location in Greater OKC. 1 mile away from Commercial Centers , Leading Hospitals / Great Restaurants /  . At the borderline of Canadian County Line and OKC.  Perfectly maintained Home , high quality fence w/ well manicured lawn , sophisticated bushes , roses galore . Corner Lot . Ready for Occupancy . Primary BR w/ big Walk-In Closet .  Two Full BA with modern Bidet , First Class Wide Shower heads & Classy Cabinetry / Spacious Closets. Classic Vinyl Wooden Flooring.  Modern interior designed Lightings all over the house & Matching Draperies . One Floor Only for easy access to all rooms. All appliances to stay plus Stainless Maytag Ref & Sharp Microwave . Big Gorgeous Lake within the Meadow Lake Community adjacent to relatively New Playground. Neat roads with wonderful, quiet & professional neighbors . Ranked the Best School in OK : Yukon School District.
Can You ASK FOR MORE ?
